呗"}, "reranked_count": 4, "plan_budget_hint": {"answer_type": "general", "boost_pricing": false, "demote_doc_types": [], "ensure_doc_types": ["faq", "pricing", "howto", "docs"], "hard_requirements": [], "page_kind_weights": {"howto": 1.08, "product_page": 1.1}, "preferred_sources": ["conversation"], "diversity_doc_types": ["howto", "faq"], "preferred_page_kinds": ["product_page", "howto"], "product_family_hints": [], "supporting_page_kinds": ["faq", "pricing_table"], "product_family_weights": {}, "active_hard_requirements": [], "active_required_evidence": [], "diversity_fetch_per_type": 6}, "active_hypothesis": "primary", "evidence_families": ["general_info"], "preferred_sources": ["conversation"], "primary_doc_types": ["faq", "pricing", "howto", "docs"], "retrieval_profile": "generic_profile", "intent_fetch_count": 0, "rewrite_candidates": ["给我讲解一下深度学习呗"], "diversity_doc_types": ["howto", "faq"], "evidence_signatures": {"pct_chunks_with_url": 0.0, "median_content_density": 1.0, "pct_chunks_with_number_unit": 0.0, "pct_chunks_boilerplate_gt_06": 0.0}, "diversity_bm25_count": 0, "supporting_doc_types": ["faq", "conversation"], "supporting_bm25_count": 0, "intent_fetch_doc_types": ["faq", "pricing", "howto", "docs"], "authoritative_doc_types": ["pricing", "howto"], "supporting_vector_count": 4, "diversity_doc_types_covered": []}, "evidence_summary": [{"score": 0.01639344262295082, "snippet": "标题：深度学习简介\\n\\n深度学习是机器学习的一个子集，它基于人工神经网络，尤其是深层神经网络。与传统的机器学习算法相比，深度学习能够自动从原始数据中学习特征，而无需人工设计特征提取器。\\n\\n深度学习的核心是神经网络，由多个层组成，包括输入层、隐藏层和输出层。每一层由许多神经元构成，神经元之间通过权重连接。训练过程中使用反向传播算法和梯度下降来更新权重，以最小化损失函数。", "chunk_id": "58915088-4b84-460c-a1a6-f17663ce1cdf", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://00a86016-deepseek_text_20260606_f64afa.txt"}, {"score": 0.016129032258064516, "snippet": "常见的深度学习架构包括：\\n- 卷积神经网络（CNN）：主要用于图像识别和计算机视觉任务。\\n- 循环神经网络（RNN）及其变体LSTM和GRU：用于序列数据，如自然语言处理和时间序列预测。\\n- Transformer：基于自注意力机制，已广泛应用于自然语言处理，代表模型有BERT、GPT等。\\n\\n深度学习在语音识别、图像分类、机器翻译、自动驾驶和医疗诊断等领域取得了突破性成果。然而，它需要大量的标注数据和计算资源，模型的解释性也相对较差。...", "chunk_id": "31aa5c1c-eb15-4f90-a0ec-ccea0b309c4b", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://00a86016-deepseek_text_20260606_f64afa.txt"}, {"score": 0.015873015873015872, "snippet": "这次任务证明了人类有能力进行地外探索，并在冷战太空竞赛中为美国赢得了重要胜利。整个阿波罗计划从1961年启动，到1972年阿波罗17号结束，共有12名宇航员登上月球。阿波罗11号的成功激励了后来数十年的太空探索，包括国际空间站和火星探测任务。", "chunk_id": "3969af38-efde-4dff-9669-71c3cd853249", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://bffcaa4a-deepseek_text_20260606_70e755.txt"}, {"score": 0.015625, "snippet": "标题：阿波罗11号与人类首次登月\\n\\n1969年7月20日，美国宇航局的阿波罗11号任务成功将人类送上月球。宇航员尼尔·阿姆斯特朗成为第一个踏上月球表面的人，并说出了那句名言：“这是个人的一小步，却是人类的一大步。”\\n\\n阿波罗11号的登月舱名为“鹰”，它于7月20日20:17 UTC降落在月球表面的静海。除了阿姆斯特朗，巴兹·奥尔德林也走出了登月舱，两人在月球表面活动了约2小时15分钟，收集了月球岩石和土壤样本，并插上了美国国旗。指令舱驾驶员迈克尔·科林斯则留在绕月轨道上。...", "chunk_id": "6b4a4400-8e18-4284-8e6e-020cc1edefae", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://bffcaa4a-deepseek_text_20260606_70e755.txt"}], "hypothesis_judge": {"selected_hypothesis": "primary", "attempted_hypotheses": ["primary", "primary", "primary", "primary"], "selected_evidence_families": ["general_info"], "selected_retrieval_profile": "generic_profile", "used_multi_hypothesis_judge": true}, "followup_questions": [], "termination_reason": "done", "llm_usage_breakdown": [{"input": 1350, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 512, "cost_usd": 0.001443}, {"input": 1260, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 512, "cost_usd": 0.001398}, {"input": 1390, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 320, "cost_usd": 0.001175}, {"input": 526, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 150, "cost_usd": 0.000488}, {"input": 992, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 400, "cost_usd": 0.001096}, {"input": 2253, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 1453, "cost_usd": 0.003306}]}
