ording to our refund policy, you are eligible for a full refund within 30 days of purchase. Contact support@example.com to request. Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days.\\",\\n  \\"followup_questions\\": [],\\n  \\"citations\\": [{\\"chunk_id\\": \\"abc123\\", \\"source_url\\": \\"https://example.com/refund\\", \\"doc_type\\": \\"policy\\"}],\\n  \\"confidence\\": 0.95\\n}\\n\\nEXAMPLE 2 (plans/pricing – include links):\\nUser question: What Windows VPS plans do you have? Price?\\nEvidence: [Chunk xyz] Source: https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale Type: pricing Content: Plan US1: $8/mo, 1GB RAM... Order: https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale/us1\\n\\n{\\n  \\"decision\\": \\"PASS\\",\\n  \\"answer\\": \\"Here are our Windows VPS plans with prices and links:\\\\n\\\\n• **US1**: $8/mo – 1GB RAM, 25GB SSD – https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale/us1\\\\n• **US2**: $16/mo – 2GB RAM, 40GB SSD – https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale/us2\\\\n• **Budget Windows VPS page**: https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale\\",\\n  \\"followup_questions\\": [],\\n  \\"citations\\": [{\\"chunk_id\\": \\"xyz\\", \\"source_url\\": \\"https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale\\", \\"doc_type\\": \\"pricing\\"}],\\n  \\"confidence\\": 0.9\\n}\\n\\nEvidence chunks will be provided in the user message.\\n\\n\\nINTERNAL ROUTING NOTES:\\n- The runtime calibrates output mode as PASS_EXACT, PASS_PARTIAL, or ASK_USER.\\n- PASS_PARTIAL is a bounded-answer mode. In JSON output, still use decision=\\"PASS\\".\\n- For PASS_PARTIAL: use natural, client-friendly language. When unclear, say briefly (e.g. \\"We don't have that\\")—no long disclaimers or lists of missing items. At most one short follow-up question.\\n\\nROUTING DECISION: CANDIDATE_VERIFY.\\nGenerate structured AnswerCandidate JSON in this pass. Do not output free-form prose.\\nReturn JSON only with this schema:\\n{\\n  \\"candidate\\": {\\n    \\"answer_type\\": \\"general\\",\\n    \\"target_entity\\": null,\\n    \\"answer_expectation\\": \\"exact|best_effort|clarify_first\\",\\n    \\"acceptable_related_types\\": [],\\n    \\"answer_mode\\": \\"PASS_PARTIAL\\",\\n    \\"support_level\\": \\"strong|partial|weak\\",\\n    \\"answer_text\\": \\"final answer text or clarification request\\",\\n    \\"citations\\": [{\\"chunk_id\\": \\"...\\", \\"source_url\\": \\"...\\", \\"doc_type\\": \\"...\\"}],\\n    \\"confidence\\": 0.0,\\n    \\"followup_questions\\": [],\\n    \\"disclaimers\\": [],\\n    \\"metadata\\": {}\\n  }\\n}\\nFor PASS_PARTIAL: keep only supported facts. Use natural, conversational tone.\\nFor PASS_PARTIAL: when info is unclear or missing, say briefly (e.g. 'We don't have that' or 'I couldn't find that')—no long disclaimers or lists of missing items.\\nFor PASS_PARTIAL: at most one short disclaimer in candidate.disclaimers; at most one followup question.\\nKnown missing (context only; do not list in answer—say briefly we don't have that): missing_evidence."}, "quality_report": {"quality_score": 0.0, "feature_scores": {}, "missing_signals": ["missing_evidence"], "hard_requirement_coverage": {}}, "retrieval_plan": {"reason": "retry_precision", "fetch_n": 100, "profile": "generic_profile", "rerank_k": 12, "attempt_index": 4}, "retry_strategy": {"query_source": "base_query", "retrieval_profile": "generic_profile", "rewrite_candidates": ["给我讲解一下深度学习呗"], "selected_retrieval_query": "给我讲解一下深度学习呗"}, "decision_router": {"lane": "CANDIDATE_VERIFY", "reason": "partial_sufficient", "decision": "PASS", "reason_human": "Partial evidence; bounded answer allowed", "answer_policy": "bounded"}, "retrieval_stats": {"fusion": "rrf", "attempt": 4, "bm25_count": 0, "plan_reason": "retry_precision", "merged_count": 4, "query_source": "provided_plan", "vector_count": 4, "query_rewrite": {"keyword_query": "给我讲解一下深度学习呗", "semantic_query": "给我讲解一下深度学习呗"}, "reranked_count": 4, "plan_budget_hint": {"answer_type": "general", "boost_pricing": false, "demote_doc_types": [], "ensure_doc_types": ["faq", "pricing", "howto", "docs"], "hard_requirements": [], "page_kind_weights": {"howto": 1.08, "product_page": 1.1}, "preferred_sources": ["conversation"], "diversity_doc_types": ["howto", "faq"], "preferred_page_kinds": ["product_page", "howto"], "product_family_hints": [], "supporting_page_kinds": ["faq", "pricing_table"], "product_family_weights": {}, "active_hard_requirements": [], "active_required_evidence": [], "diversity_fetch_per_type": 6}, "active_hypothesis": "primary", "evidence_families": ["general_info"], "preferred_sources": ["conversation"], "primary_doc_types": ["faq", "pricing", "howto", "docs"], "retrieval_profile": "generic_profile", "intent_fetch_count": 0, "rewrite_candidates": ["给我讲解一下深度学习呗"], "diversity_doc_types": ["howto", "faq"], "evidence_signatures": {"pct_chunks_with_url": 0.0, "median_content_density": 1.0, "pct_chunks_with_number_unit": 0.0, "pct_chunks_boilerplate_gt_06": 0.0}, "diversity_bm25_count": 0, "supporting_doc_types": ["faq", "conversation"], "supporting_bm25_count": 0, "intent_fetch_doc_types": ["faq", "pricing", "howto", "docs"], "authoritative_doc_types": ["pricing", "howto"], "supporting_vector_count": 4, "diversity_doc_types_covered": []}, "evidence_summary": [{"score": 0.01639344262295082, "snippet": "标题：深度学习简介\\n\\n深度学习是机器学习的一个子集，它基于人工神经网络，尤其是深层神经网络。与传统的机器学习算法相比，深度学习能够自动从原始数据中学习特征，而无需人工设计特征提取器。\\n\\n深度学习的核心是神经网络，由多个层组成，包括输入层、隐藏层和输出层。每一层由许多神经元构成，神经元之间通过权重连接。训练过程中使用反向传播算法和梯度下降来更新权重，以最小化损失函数。", "chunk_id": "58915088-4b84-460c-a1a6-f17663ce1cdf", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://00a86016-deepseek_text_20260606_f64afa.txt"}, {"score": 0.016129032258064516, "snippet": "常见的深度学习架构包括：\\n- 卷积神经网络（CNN）：主要用于图像识别和计算机视觉任务。\\n- 循环神经网络（RNN）及其变体LSTM和GRU：用于序列数据，如自然语言处理和时间序列预测。\\n- Transformer：基于自注意力机制，已广泛应用于自然语言处理，代表模型有BERT、GPT等。\\n\\n深度学习在语音识别、图像分类、机器翻译、自动驾驶和医疗诊断等领域取得了突破性成果。然而，它需要大量的标注数据和计算资源，模型的解释性也相对较差。...", "chunk_id": "31aa5c1c-eb15-4f90-a0ec-ccea0b309c4b", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://00a86016-deepseek_text_20260606_f64afa.txt"}, {"score": 0.015873015873015872, "snippet": "这次任务证明了人类有能力进行地外探索，并在冷战太空竞赛中为美国赢得了重要胜利。整个阿波罗计划从1961年启动，到1972年阿波罗17号结束，共有12名宇航员登上月球。阿波罗11号的成功激励了后来数十年的太空探索，包括国际空间站和火星探测任务。", "chunk_id": "3969af38-efde-4dff-9669-71c3cd853249", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://bffcaa4a-deepseek_text_20260606_70e755.txt"}, {"score": 0.015625, "snippet": "标题：阿波罗11号与人类首次登月\\n\\n1969年7月20日，美国宇航局的阿波罗11号任务成功将人类送上月球。宇航员尼尔·阿姆斯特朗成为第一个踏上月球表面的人，并说出了那句名言：“这是个人的一小步，却是人类的一大步。”\\n\\n阿波罗11号的登月舱名为“鹰”，它于7月20日20:17 UTC降落在月球表面的静海。除了阿姆斯特朗，巴兹·奥尔德林也走出了登月舱，两人在月球表面活动了约2小时15分钟，收集了月球岩石和土壤样本，并插上了美国国旗。指令舱驾驶员迈克尔·科林斯则留在绕月轨道上。...", "chunk_id": "6b4a4400-8e18-4284-8e6e-020cc1edefae", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://bffcaa4a-deepseek_text_20260606_70e755.txt"}], "hypothesis_judge": {"selected_hypothesis": "primary", "attempted_hypotheses": ["primary", "primary", "primary", "primary"], "selected_evidence_families": ["general_info"], "selected_retrieval_profile": "generic_profile", "used_multi_hypothesis_judge": true}, "followup_questions": ["您对深度学习中的哪种架构或应用更感兴趣？"], "termination_reason": "done", "llm_usage_breakdown": [{"input": 1194, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 512, "cost_usd": 0.001365}, {"input": 1234, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 320, "cost_usd": 0.001097}, {"input": 370, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 150, "cost_usd": 0.00041}, {"input": 2095, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 1327, "cost_usd": 0.003038}]}
