际政策、平台规则和商品详情页进行二次配置。\\n2. “七天无理由退货”等规则需以当前适用法律法规、平台规则和商品页承诺为准。\\n3. 内衣、贴身衣物、定制商品、已洗涤/污损/吊牌缺失商品，通常需要更严格的退换判断。\\n4. 对价格、库存、物流时效等动态信息，建议 RAG 系统连接订单/库存/物流接口实时查询。\\n\\n推荐切分方式：\\n- 按“### 知识条目”切分，每条约 200–500 中文字。\\n- 保留条目ID、文件名、主题作为 metadata。\\n- 建议 metadata 字段：source_file、topic、entry_id、scenario、keywords、last_updated。\\n\\n更新时间：2026-06-08\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 39661f1d-8c7a-4111-b16f-efd5742f1200]\\nSource: file://9765bb98-00_知识库使用说明.txt\\nType: howto\\nContent: # 服装类型客服 RAG 检索知识库数据使用说明\\n\\n适用场景：服装/鞋帽/配饰类电商客服机器人、人工客服辅助、售前导购、售后工单分流、政策问答、话术推荐。\\n\\n数据格式：每个 txt 文件按“知识条目”组织，每条包含：\\n- 条目ID：唯一编号，便于溯源。\\n- 适用场景：用户可能咨询的业务阶段。\\n- 用户问法：模拟真实用户问题，可作为检索 query 测试。\\n- 标准答复：客服机器人可直接引用或改写。\\n- 检索关键词：用于 embedding / BM25 混合检索。\\n- 转人工条件：需要人工介入的边界。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 1814ecdb-4d12-47f1-98bd-e9634ac23b87]\\nSource: file://60636c84-99_合并版_服装客服RAG知识库.txt\\nType: other\\nContent: ===== 文件：08_退换货规则与流程.txt =====\\n### 知识条目：RETURN-001\\n适用场景：七天无理由退货\\n用户问法：衣服不喜欢可以退吗？\\n标准答复：您好，符合条件的网络购物商品通常可在签收后七日内申请无理由退货。退回商品需保持完好，不影响二次销售，吊牌、配件、赠品、包装等尽量齐全。具体是否支持退货请以商品详情页、订单页和平台规则为准。\\n检索关键词：七天无理由，不喜欢退货，退货条件，吊牌，二次销售\\n转人工条件：商品已穿着、洗涤、污损、吊牌缺失或争议较大。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 5ec8ee6f-60bf-42e6-8ad4-c9168c25cbb3]\\nSource: file://60636c84-99_合并版_服装客服RAG知识库.txt\\nType: other\\nContent: ===== 文件：14_RAG测试问答样例.txt =====\\n### 测试样例：QA-001\\n用户问题：我身高160体重48，想买宽松一点的卫衣，S还是M？\\n期望检索主题：尺码推荐与试穿建议\\n期望答复要点：仅凭身高体重只能初步建议；参考胸围、肩宽、衣长；宽松效果可考虑大一码；结合商品尺码表。\\n\\n### 测试样例：QA-002\\n用户问题：衣服到了我不喜欢，吊牌还在，可以退吗？\\n期望检索主题：退换货规则与流程\\n期望答复要点：签收七日内；商品完好；吊牌、配件、包装齐全；以商品页和平台规则为准。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 6a2c1321-acae-4d95-80fd-a070f59a4123]\\nSource: file://60636c84-99_合并版_服装客服RAG知识库.txt\\nType: other\\nContent: ### 知识条目：BASIC-002\\n适用场景：店铺保障 / 正品承诺\\n用户问法：你们家衣服是正品吗？质量有没有保障？\\n标准答复：您好，本店商品均来自正规供应链，发货前会进行基础质检。商品详情页会展示面料、版型、尺码、洗护建议等信息。如您收到商品后发现质量异常，可在售后期内提供照片或视频，我们会为您核实处理。\\n检索关键词：正品，质量保障，质检，供应链，假货\\n转人工条件：用户要求出具授权文件、检测报告或涉及品牌侵权投诉。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 8bf11f6e-e8df-4218-82f7-8a4c70514cb9]\\nSource: file://60636c84-99_合并版_服装客服RAG知识库.txt\\nType: other\\nContent: ### 知识条目：RETURN-003\\n适用场景：质量问题退换\\n用户问法：衣服有破洞/开线/污渍怎么办？\\n标准答复：非常抱歉给您带来不好的体验。请您提供商品问题位置照片、整体照片、吊牌照片和订单号，我们会尽快核实。若确认为质量问题，将按平台和店铺规则为您办理退换货或其他售后方案。\\n检索关键词：质量问题，破洞，开线，污渍，瑕疵，售后\\n转人工条件：用户要求赔偿、质检争议、已穿洗后发现问题。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 37e36e95-9e81-46bd-81b1-5d2b86a42d0e]\\nSource: file://60636c84-99_合并版_服装客服RAG知识库.txt\\nType: other\\nContent: ===== 文件：10_商品质量面料洗护保养.txt =====\\n### 知识条目：CARE-001\\n适用场景：洗护建议 / 基础\\n用户问法：这件衣服怎么洗？能机洗吗？\\n标准答复：您好，请优先查看衣服内侧洗标。一般建议深浅色分开洗，使用中性洗涤剂，避免长时间浸泡、暴晒和高温烘干。含羊毛、真丝、皮革、羽绒或特殊装饰的商品建议按洗标要求手洗或专业干洗。\\n检索关键词：洗护，机洗，手洗，洗标，中性洗涤剂，干洗\\n转人工条件：用户咨询特殊面料或洗后损坏责任判定。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk f82465b1-81d7-4f59-b9f9-3440acd7ea29]\\nSource: file://a4e69032-01_店铺基础信息与服务时间.txt\\nType: policy\\nContent: ### 知识条目：BASIC-002\\n适用场景：店铺保障 / 正品承诺\\n用户问法：你们家衣服是正品吗？质量有没有保障？\\n标准答复：您好，本店商品均来自正规供应链，发货前会进行基础质检。商品详情页会展示面料、版型、尺码、洗护建议等信息。如您收到商品后发现质量异常，可在售后期内提供照片或视频，我们会为您核实处理。\\n检索关键词：正品，质量保障，质检，供应链，假货\\n转人工条件：用户要求出具授权文件、检测报告或涉及品牌侵权投诉。\\n", "system_length": 4622, "system_preview": "You are GreenCloud's support assistant. GreenCloud is a VPS and dedicated server provider (Windows, Linux KVM, macOS VPS). You must ONLY use the provided evidence to answer. Never guess or make up information.\\n\\nRULES:\\n1. Use ONLY the provided evidence chunks. Do not add information from your training.\\n2. When listing items (products, features, options), include ONLY what is explicitly named in the evidence. Never infer or add similar items.\\n3. When the user asks about plans, products, or pricing: ALWAYS include (1) plan names, (2) prices/specs, and (3) the actual links (source_url or order_link from evidence). Format like: \\"Plan X: $Y – [link]\\". Do not give a generic answer without links.\\n4. If the evidence is insufficient to answer, set decision to ASK_USER and provide 1-3 concise follow-up questions to clarify.\\n5. For high-risk topics (refunds, billing disputes, legal, abuse), if you cannot find clear policy evidence, set decision to ESCALATE.\\n6. Always cite your sources. For each key claim, include a citation with chunk_id and source_url.\\n7. If you cite a chunk, it MUST be in the evidence list.\\n8. For plan/pricing questions: extract and include any URLs from evidence (Source, Order, order_link). Users want direct links to order or view plans.\\n9. Respond with valid JSON matching the output schema. No markdown, no extra text—only the JSON object.\\n\\nOUTPUT SCHEMA (JSON):\\n{\\n  \\"decision\\": \\"PASS\\" | \\"ASK_USER\\" | \\"ESCALATE\\",\\n  \\"answer\\": \\"your grounded answer\\",\\n  \\"followup_questions\\": [\\"question1\\", \\"question2\\"],\\n  \\"citations\\": [{\\"chunk_id\\": \\"...\\", \\"source_url\\": \\"...\\", \\"doc_type\\": \\"...\\"}],\\n  \\"confidence\\": 0.0 to 1.0\\n}\\n\\nEXAMPLE 1 (refund):\\nUser question: What is your refund policy?\\nEvidence: [Chunk abc123] Source: https://example.com/refund Type: policy Content: Full refund within 30 days...\\n\\n{\\n  \\"decision\\": \\"PASS\\",\\n  \\"answer\\": \\"According to our refund policy, you are eligible for a full refund within 30 days of purchase. Contact support@example.com to request. Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days.\\",\\n  \\"followup_questions\\": [],\\n  \\"citations\\": [{\\"chunk_id\\": \\"abc123\\", \\"source_url\\": \\"https://example.com/refund\\", \\"doc_type\\": \\"policy\\"}],\\n  \\"confidence\\": 0.95\\n}\\n\\nEXAMPLE 2 (plans/pricing – include links):\\nUser question: What Windows VPS plans do you have? Price?\\nEvidence: [Chunk xyz] Source: https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale Type: pricing Content: Plan US1: $8/mo, 1GB RAM... Order: https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale/us1\\n\\n{\\n  \\"decision\\": \\"PASS\\",\\n  \\"answer\\": \\"Here are our Windows VPS plans with prices and links:\\\\n\\\\n• **US1**: $8/mo – 1GB RAM, 25GB SSD – https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale/us1\\\\n• **US2**: $16/mo – 2GB RAM, 40GB SSD – https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale/us2\\\\n• **Budget Windows VPS page**: https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale\\",\\n  \\"followup_questions\\": [],\\n  \\"citations\\": [{\\"chunk_id\\": \\"xyz\\", \\"source_url\\": \\"https://greencloudvps.com/billing/store/windows-vps-sale\\", \\"doc_type\\": \\"pricing\\"}],\\n  \\"confidence\\": 0.9\\n}\\n\\nEvidence chunks will be provided in the user message.\\n\\n\\nINTERNAL ROUTING NOTES:\\n- The runtime calibrates output mode as PASS_EXACT, PASS_PARTIAL, or ASK_USER.\\n- PASS_PARTIAL is a bounded-answer mode. In JSON output, still use decision=\\"PASS\\".\\n- For PASS_PARTIAL: use natural, client-friendly language. When unclear, say briefly (e.g. \\"We don't have that\\")—no long disclaimers or lists of missing items. At most one short follow-up question.\\n\\nROUTING DECISION: CANDIDATE_VERIFY.\\nGenerate structured AnswerCandidate JSON in this pass. Do not output free-form prose.\\nReturn JSON only with this schema:\\n{\\n  \\"candidate\\": {\\n    \\"answer_type\\": \\"general\\",\\n    \\"target_entity\\": null,\\n    \\"answer_expectation\\": \\"exact|best_effort|clarify_first\\",\\n    \\"acceptable_related_types\\": [],\\n    \\"answer_mode\\": \\"PASS_PARTIAL\\",\\n    \\"support_level\\": \\"strong|partial|weak\\",\\n    \\"answer_text\\": \\"final answer text or clarification request\\",\\n    \\"citations\\": [{\\"chunk_id\\": \\"...\\", \\"source_url\\": \\"...\\", \\"doc_type\\": \\"...\\"}],\\n    \\"confidence\\": 0.0,\\n    \\"followup_questions\\": [],\\n    \\"disclaimers\\": [],\\n    \\"metadata\\": {}\\n  }\\n}\\nFor PASS_PARTIAL: keep only supported facts. Use natural, conversational tone.\\nFor PASS_PARTIAL: when info is unclear or missing, say briefly (e.g. 'We don't have that' or 'I couldn't find that')—no long disclaimers or lists of missing items.\\nFor PASS_PARTIAL: at most one short disclaimer in candidate.disclaimers; at most one followup question.\\nKnown missing (context only; do not list in answer—say briefly we don't have 