丝、皮革、羽绒或特殊装饰的商品建议按洗标要求手洗或专业干洗。\\n检索关键词：洗护，机洗，手洗，洗标，中性洗涤剂，干洗\\n转人工条件：用户咨询特殊面料或洗后损坏责任判定。...", "chunk_id": "37e36e95-9e81-46bd-81b1-5d2b86a42d0e", "doc_type": "other", "source_url": "file://60636c84-99_合并版_服装客服RAG知识库.txt"}, {"score": 0.015384615384615385, "snippet": "### 知识条目：BASIC-002\\n适用场景：店铺保障 / 正品承诺\\n用户问法：你们家衣服是正品吗？质量有没有保障？\\n标准答复：您好，本店商品均来自正规供应链，发货前会进行基础质检。商品详情页会展示面料、版型、尺码、洗护建议等信息。如您收到商品后发现质量异常，可在售后期内提供照片或视频，我们会为您核实处理。\\n检索关键词：正品，质量保障，质检，供应链，假货\\n转人工条件：用户要求出具授权文件、检测报告或涉及品牌侵权投诉。...", "chunk_id": "f82465b1-81d7-4f59-b9f9-3440acd7ea29", "doc_type": "policy", "source_url": "file://a4e69032-01_店铺基础信息与服务时间.txt"}], "hypothesis_judge": {"selected_hypothesis": "primary", "attempted_hypotheses": ["primary", "primary", "primary", "primary"], "selected_evidence_families": ["general_info"], "selected_retrieval_profile": "generic_profile", "used_multi_hypothesis_judge": true}, "reviewer_reasons": ["PASS requires at least one citation"], "followup_questions": ["Could you provide more details about your question?"], "termination_reason": "ask_user", "llm_usage_breakdown": [{"input": 1160, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 512, "cost_usd": 0.001348}, {"input": 2022, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 320, "cost_usd": 0.001491}, {"input": 336, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 150, "cost_usd": 0.000393}, {"input": 3033, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 2048, "cost_usd": 0.004589}], "max_attempts_reached": true, "review_unsupported_claims": ["citations"]}
