, "doc_type": "policy", "source_url": "file://a4e69032-01_店铺基础信息与服务时间.txt"}, {"score": 0.013888888888888888, "snippet": "### 知识条目：REFUND-001\\n适用场景：退款时效\\n用户问法：退货寄回了，什么时候退款？\\n标准答复：您好，退货包裹到仓后需要进行验收，确认商品符合退货条件后会发起退款。退款通常原路退回至您的支付账户，到账时间受支付渠道影响。您可以在订单售后详情页查看当前进度。\\n检索关键词：退款，到账，退货验收，原路退回，售后进度\\n转人工条件：仓库签收超过承诺时间仍未退款。", "chunk_id": "28cbf4db-dbe2-4f25-a842-d2750fcccd96", "doc_type": "faq", "source_url": "file://152f1716-09_退款到账与售后进度.txt"}], "hypothesis_judge": {"selected_hypothesis": "fallback_capability", "attempted_hypotheses": ["hypothesis_1", "fallback_capability", "fallback_policy"], "selected_evidence_families": ["capability_availability", "pricing_limits", "policy_terms"], "selected_retrieval_profile": "pricing_profile", "used_multi_hypothesis_judge": true}, "followup_questions": ["请问您的订单号是多少？我可以帮您查询具体的物流状态。"], "termination_reason": "done", "llm_usage_breakdown": [{"input": 1733, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 410, "cost_usd": 0.001481}, {"input": 1214, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 350, "cost_usd": 0.001132}, {"input": 1679, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 117, "cost_usd": 0.001015}, {"input": 3621, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 347, "cost_usd": 0.002331}, {"input": 2046, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 96, "cost_usd": 0.001167}, {"input": 3227, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 440, "cost_usd": 0.002273}, {"input": 1997, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 113, "cost_usd": 0.001168}, {"input": 926, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 44, "cost_usd": 0.000529}, {"input": 2204, "model": "mimo-v2.5", "output": 239, "cost_usd": 0.00146}], "conversation_relevance": {"reason": "The current question about shipping time is unrelated to the previous discussion about product defects, returns, and care.", "relevant": false, "relevant_turn_count": 0}}
