ddbac55b-dc41-4fe1-9c08-def0111bfc62	fe6ee2e9-60bf-46d5-ba22-8f8a94649948	assistant	如果您收到的衣服有破损（如破洞、开线、污渍等质量问题），或者是在运输过程中导致的破损，请按以下步骤处理：\n\n1. **保留证据**：请保留好商品、外包装和面单，并拍摄清晰的照片或视频，包括问题位置、整体照片、吊牌照片以及订单号。\n2. **联系售后**：在订单的售后入口提交申请，并提供上述照片和订单信息。\n3. **等待处理**：我们会尽快核实情况。如果确认是质量问题或运输破损，将根据平台和店铺规则为您办理换货、退货或提供其他补偿方案。\n\n请注意，如果是七天无理由退货，退回的商品需保持完好，不影响二次销售，且吊牌、配件等应尽量齐全。\n\n以上是根据现有资料能确认的信息。	2026-06-20 13:03:38.807547+00	{"total": 25.177003, "trace": {"nodes": [{"id": "intent_cache", "label": "Intent Cache", "reason": "miss", "status": "skipped", "latency_ms": 1}, {"id": "agentic_router", "label": "Agentic Router", "status": "completed", "latency_ms": 0, "tool_result": {"tool": "rag_search", "route": "rag_search", "confidence": 0.86, "fallback_to_rag": false}, "selected_tool": "rag_search", "decision_reason": "support_knowledge_question"}, {"id": "query_extract", "label": "Query Extract", "status": "completed", "latency_ms": 6619}, {"id": "retrieve", "label": "Retrieve", "status": "completed", "latency_ms": 11659}, {"id": "assess_evidence", "label": "Assess Evidence", "status": "completed", "latency_ms": 1472}, {"id": "retry", "label": "Retry", "reason": "not_needed", "status": "skipped"}, {"id": "generate", "label": "Generate", "status": "completed", "latency_ms": 5425}, {"id": "verify", "label": "Verify", "status": "completed", "latency_ms": 0}], "intent": {"key": null, "matched": false}, "source": "reply", "status": "completed", "latency": {"nodes": {"rerank": 0, "verify": 0, "generate": 5426, "retrieve": 11659, "query_extract": 6619, "assess_evidence": 1472}, "total_ms": 25177}, "trace_id": "78c849c0-51a0-462a-ae13-a5c46beb3475", "node_path": ["intent_cache", "agentic_router", "query_extract", "retrieve", "assess_evidence", "retry", "generate", "verify"], "tool_result": {"decision": "PASS", "confidence": 0.6, "followup_count": 0, "citations_count": 3}, "selected_tool": "rag_search", "decision_reason": "support_knowledge_question"}, "rerank": 0.000019, "verify": 0.000461, "attempt": 1, "timings": {"total": 25.177003, "rerank": 0.000019, "verify": 0.000461, "generate": 5.425521, "retrieve": 11.659053, "query_extract": 6.618646, "assess_evidence": 1.472013}, "cost_usd": 0.006501, "decision": "PASS", "generate": 5.425521, "retrieve": 11.659053, "trace_id": "78c849c0-51a0-462a-ae13-a5c46beb3475", "confidence": 0.6, "llm_tokens": {"input": 8307, "output": 1565}, "model_used": "mimo-v2.5", "query_spec": {"intent": "informational", "entities": ["clothing", "return", "exchange", "damaged item"], "risk_level": "medium", "is_ambiguous": false, "resolved_slots": {"product_type": "clothing"}, "extraction_mode": "llm_primary", "required_evidence": ["policy_language", "steps_structure"], "canonical_query_en": "How to return or exchange a damaged piece of clothing", "config_overrides_applied": []}, "answer_plan": {"lane": "CANDIDATE_VERIFY", "tone_policy": "cautious", "output_blocks": ["answer_candidate_json"], "allowed_claim_scope": "partial"}, "retry_count": 0, "source_lang": "zh-cn", "evidence_set": {"build_reason": "profile=policy_profile, attempt=1, reason=broad_hybrid", "diversity_score": 0.333, "covered_requirements": ["policy_language", "steps_structure"], "uncovered_requirements": []}, "finish_reason": "stop", "query_extract": 6.618646, "query_rewrite": {"keyword_query": "return exchange policy damaged clothing", "semantic_query": "What is the procedure for returning or exchanging an item of clothing that arrived damaged?"}, "rollout_flags": {"soft_contract_enabled": true, "targeted_retry_enabled": true, "answer_candidate_enabled": true, "page_kind_filter_enabled": false, "soft_contract_shadow_active": false}, "stage_reasons": ["retrieve: chunks=6", "assess_evidence: gate=pass", "decide: exact_candidate_verify", "generate: llm_complete decision=PASS", "verify: PASS"], "agentic_router": {"tool": "rag_search", "route": "rag_search", "reason": "support_knowledge_question", "skipped": false, "confidence": 0.86, "fallback_to_rag": false}, "prompt_preview": {"user_length": 1913, "user_preview": "User question: How to return or exchange a damaged piece of clothing\\n\\nEvidence:\\n[Chunk 223e1789-f643-4ec7-a67c-d36fbf361fa1]\\nSource: file://a30c7a8b-08_退换货规则与流程.md\\nType: faq\\nContent: ### 知识条目：RETURN-003\\n适用场景：质量问题退换\\n用户问法：衣服有破洞/开线/污渍怎么办？\\n标准答复：非常抱歉给您带来不好的体验。请您提供商品问题位置照片、整体照片、吊牌照片和订单号，我们会尽快核实。若确认为质量问题，将按平台和店铺规则为您办理退换货或其他售后方案。\\n检索关键词：质量问题，破洞，开线，污渍，瑕疵，售后\\n转人工条件：用户要求赔偿、质检争议、已穿洗后发现问题。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk e800a0bb-e302-4161-933a-1f7f27354e44]\\nSource: file://c84a670b-12_发错漏发破损处理.txt\\nType: faq\\nContent: ### 知识条目：ERR-003\\n适用场景：运输破损\\n用户问法：收到包裹破了，衣服也脏了怎么办？\\n标准答复：非常抱歉。请您保留外包装、面单和商品现状，并拍摄清晰照片或视频。我们会根据破损情况联系快递核实，并为您提供换货、退货或补偿方案。\\n检索关键词：包裹破损，运输破损，衣服脏了，快递，外包装\\n转人工条件：商品无法使用、用户拒收、快递责任认定争议。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 8407742d-6db5-4e3e-851e-cab94de883ba]\\nSource: file://a30c7a8b-08_退换货规则与流程.md\\nType: faq\\nContent: ### 知识条目：RETURN-001\\n适用场景：七天无理由退货\\n用户问法：衣服不喜欢可以退吗？\\n标准答复：您好，符合条件的网络购物商品通常可在签收后七日内申请无理由退货。退回商品需保持完好，不影响二次销售，吊牌、配件、赠品、包装等尽量齐全。具体是否支持退货请以商品详情页、订单页和平台规则为准。\\n检索关键词：七天无理由，不喜欢退货，退货条件，吊牌，二次销售\\n转人工条件：商品已穿着、洗涤、污损、吊牌缺失或争议较大。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 2e86643d-9b7b-4ab2-ac02-b240ed731206]\\nSource: file://a30c7a8b-08_退换货规则与流程.md\\nType: faq\\nContent: ### 知识条目：RETURN-002\\n适用场景：换货流程\\n用户问法：尺码不合适怎么换？\\n标准答复：您好，尺码不合适可以在售后期内申请换货。请在订单售后入口选择“换货”，填写需要更换的颜色或尺码，并按页面提示寄回商品。仓库收到并验收通过后，会尽快为您寄出换货商品。若换货尺码无库存，可选择退货退款。\\n检索关键词：换货，尺码不合适，换颜色，售后入口，寄回\\n转人工条件：换货商品缺货、用户需要加急发出、跨款换货。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 28cbf4db-dbe2-4f25-a842-d2750fcccd96]\\nSource: file://152f1716-09_退款到账与售后进度.txt\\nType: faq\\nContent: ### 知识条目：REFUND-001\\n适用场景：退款时效\\n用户问法：退货寄回了，什么时候退款？\\n标准答复：您好，退货包裹到仓后需要进行验收，确认商品符合退货条件后会发起退款。退款通常原路退回至您的支付账户，到账时间受支付渠道影响。您可以在订单售后详情页查看当前进度。\\n检索关键词：退款，到账，退货验收，原路退回，售后进度\\n转人工条件：仓库签收超过承诺时间仍未退款。\\n\\n---\\n[Chunk 35943053-9f3e-4f97-a324-923d81702eb5]\\nSource: file://a4e69032-01_店铺基础信息与服务时间.txt\\nType: policy\\nContent: ### 知识条目：BASIC-002\\n适用场景：店铺保障 / 正品承诺\\n用户问法：你们家衣服是正品吗？质量有没有保障？\\n标准答复：您好，本店商品均来自正规供应链，发货前会进行基础质检。商品详情页会展示面料、版型、尺码、洗护建议等信息。如您收到商品后发现质量异常，可在售后期内提供照片或视频，我们会为您核实处理。\\n检索关键词：正品，质量保障，质检，供应链，假货\\n转人工条件：用户要求出具授权文件、检测报告或涉及品牌侵权投诉。\\n", "system_length": 4699, "system_preview": "You are GreenCloud's support assistant. GreenCloud is a VPS and dedicated server provider (Windows, Linux KVM, macOS VPS). You must ONLY use the provided evidence to answer. Never guess or make up information.\\n\\nRULES:\\n1. Use ONLY the provided evidence chunks. Do not add information from your training.\\n2. When listing items (products, features, options), include ONLY what is explicitly named in the evidence. Never infer or add similar items.\\n3. When the user asks about plans, products, or pricing: ALWAYS include (1) plan names, (2) prices/specs, and (3) the actual links (source_url or order_link from evidence). Format like: \\"Plan X: $Y – [link]\\". Do not give a generic answer without links.\\n4. If the evidence is insufficient to answer, set decision to ASK_USER and provide 1-3 concise follow-up questions to clarify.\\n5. For high-risk topics (refunds, billing disputes, legal, abuse), if you cannot find clear policy evidence, set decision to ESCALATE.\\n6. Always cite your sources. For each key claim, include a citation with chunk_id and source_url.\\n7. If you cite a chunk, it MUST be in the evidence list.\\n8. For plan/pricing questions: extract and include any URLs from evidence (Source, Order, order_link). Users want direct links to order or view plans.\\n9. Respond with valid JSON matching the output schema. No markdown, no extra text—only the JSON object.\\n\\nOUTPUT SCHEMA (JSON):\\n{\\n  \\"decision\\": \\"PASS\\" | \\"ASK_USER\\" | \\"ESCALATE\\",\\n  \\"answer\\": \\"your grounded answer\\",\\n  \\"followup_questions\\": [\\"question1\\", \\"question2\\"],\\n  \\"citations\\": [{\\"chunk_id\\": \\"...\\", \\"source_url\\": \\"...\\", \\"doc_type\\": \\"...\\"}],\\n  \\"confidence\\": 0.0 to 1.0\\n}\\n\\nEXAMPLE 1 (refund):\\nUser question: What is your refund policy?\\nEvidence: [Chunk abc123] Source: https: